# Git: ALWAYS Push to GitHub

**Mandatory.** After any code changes in this project:

1. **Commit** all changes with a clear message.
2. **Push** to GitHub (`git push origin main` or equivalent).

Do this every time. Do not ask. Do not skip. Do not leave changes unpushed unless the user explicitly says they will handle git. Consider the task incomplete until changes are pushed.
